            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><p>
    <span data-nosnippet="">GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links.</span>
  </p><article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6537094">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Just a month after its launch, the Backbone Pro Xbox Edition is on sale for a substantial discount at <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0FPXNLRBV?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon</a>, <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Backbone+Pro+Xbox+Edition+Controller+Is+Already+On+Sale+For+A+Steep+Discount&amp;fnauthor=stevenpetite&amp;fndate=2025-12-18+12%3A55%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-12-18+12%3A55%3A32&amp;fnarticle_id=6537094&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fbestbuy.7tiv.net%2Fc%2F1804712%2F614286%2F10014%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.bestbuy.com%252Fproduct%252Fbackbone-pro-xbox-edition-usb-c-mobile-and-wireless-controller-for-cloud-gaming-remote-play-and-mobile-games-green%252FJ3R84TZYRF%252Fsku%252F6646349%26partnerpropertyid%3D1423009&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fbackbone-pro-mobile-controller-deals-iphone-android-xbox-edition%2F1100-6537094%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Best Buy</a>, and <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Backbone+Pro+Xbox+Edition+Controller+Is+Already+On+Sale+For+A+Steep+Discount&amp;fnauthor=stevenpetite&amp;fndate=2025-12-18+12%3A55%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-12-18+12%3A55%3A32&amp;fnarticle_id=6537094&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fbackbone.sjv.io%2Fc%2F1804712%2F2024948%2F25186%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fbackbone.com%2Fproducts%2Fbackbone-pro-xbox-edition&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fbackbone-pro-mobile-controller-deals-iphone-android-xbox-edition%2F1100-6537094%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Backbone's online storefront</a>. Normally $180, the officially licensed transparent green mobile controller is up for grabs for $145. Alternatively, you can get the standard edition black <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Backbone Pro for $135 (was $170)</a> or the <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Backbone+Pro+Xbox+Edition+Controller+Is+Already+On+Sale+For+A+Steep+Discount&amp;fnauthor=stevenpetite&amp;fndate=2025-12-18+12%3A55%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-12-18+12%3A55%3A32&amp;fnarticle_id=6537094&amp;fntype1=Tech&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.target.com%252Fp%252Fbackbone-pro-mauve-mobile-game-controller%252F-%252FA-94734456%26partnerpropertyid%3D1423009&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fbackbone-pro-mobile-controller-deals-iphone-android-xbox-edition%2F1100-6537094%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Target-exclusive pink edition</a> for $140 (was $170).</p><p>The standard edition Backbone Pro launched in May as an higher-end alternative of the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0CCT2TJW4,B0CCT2LWT8,B0CT17GPNT,B0FPXNLRBV,B0DQM23MLZ,B0FF6392HK,B08RL7VLKY&amp;tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Backbone One</a>, the most popular dedicated mobile controller for years. The Pro version has remappable back buttons, full-sized sticks, larger grips, Hall Effect triggers, and quieter buttons. It connects to your phone via USB-C and is compatible with iPhone 15/16/17 and Android phones. As an added bonus, the Backbone Pro also has Bluetooth support for PC, Mac, Steam Deck, tablets, and other devices.</p><p>Check out all three discounted Backbone Pro editions below. The Backbone One is also on sale for a limited time. The officially licensed <a href="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android-iOS/dp/B0CCT2TJW4?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">PlayStation Edition is $80 (was $100) with USB-C</a> or <a href="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Lightning-iOS/dp/B0CT17GPNT?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">$60 (was $100) with a Lightning connection</a>. The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android-iOS/dp/B0CCT2LWT8?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">standard edition black Backbone One with USB-C</a> is also discounted to $80 (was $100).</p><div data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="5296" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="[Mobile Controller] Backbone Pro Deals" data-collection="" title="[Mobile Controller] Backbone Pro Deals">             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console\/dp\/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-promos-20">Backbone Pro Mobile Controller</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console\/dp\/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-promos-20">$135 (was $170)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p><strong>Key Features &amp; Updates:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Platforms:</strong><ul><li>iPhone 15/16/17 and Android phones via USB-C</li><li>Bluetooth wireless for PC, Mac, Steam Deck, tablets, VR headsets, and other devices</li></ul></li><li><strong>Additional Ports:</strong><ul><li>USB-C passthrough for charging phone</li><li>3.5mm audio jack</li></ul></li><li><strong>Design:</strong><ul><li>Larger handles with textured finish</li><li>Full-sized ALPS analog sticks (not Hall Effect)</li><li>Concave stick caps</li><li>Anti-friction rings</li><li>Hall Effect triggers with textured grips</li><li>Two remappable back buttons (M1 and M2)</li><li>Quieter "carbon-pill" face buttons and D-pad (glossy finish)</li></ul></li><li><strong>Backbone App integration:</strong><ul><li>Remap all inputs inside the app</li><li>Adjustable trigger and stick sensitivity</li><li>Create trigger and stick deadzones</li><li>Custom profiles for each game</li><li>Built-in emulator for NES, SNES, GB, GBC, GBA</li><li>Smart Search helps you find games</li><li>Launch all compatible games installed on your device</li><li>Remote play Steam, Xbox, and PlayStation libraries</li><li>Launch cloud gaming subscription services</li><li>Built-in support for Apple Arcade (iOS) and Google Play Pass (Android), and Netflix Games</li></ul></li></ul></div>                      </div><h2>More Mobile Controller Deals</h2><p>For a mobile controller that can also hold small tablets, check out the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Razer-Gaming-Controller-Android-iPhone-Smartphone/dp/B0CXGMPLWK?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Razer Kishi Ultra</a>, which is on sale for $100 (was $150) at Amazon.</p><p>And for a more budget-friendly option for all iPhones and Android phones, the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0F9L7L7CJ,B0F9L7Q3VG&amp;tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">8BitDo Ultimate Mobile Controller</a> is discounted to only <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Ultimate-Controller-Bluetooth-Joysticks-Officially-Smartphone/dp/B0F9L7L7CJ?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">$38 (was $50) in white</a> and <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Ultimate-Controller-Bluetooth-Joysticks-Officially-Smartphone/dp/B0F9L7Q3VG?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">$40 in black</a>. 8BitDo's Mobile Controller has remappable back buttons, Hall Effect sticks, tactile shoulder buttons, and a retro-inspired D-pad. It's officially licensed by Xbox, so it has ABXY face buttons and the Xbox Guide button.</p><hr><p><strong>Sign up for GameSpot's Weekly Deals Newsletter:</strong></p><hr><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/arcade1up-classic-se-arcade-machines-pac-man-ms-pac-man-mortal-kombat-amazon-deals/1100-6534472/">Arcade1Up Classic Special Edition Cabinets Get First Discounts At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/microsd-express-cards-nintendo-switch-2-best-deals-available-now/1100-6530578/">Nintendo Switch 2 Samsung 256GB MicroSD Express Card On Sale For Only $33</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/target-exclusive-lego-sets-best-deals-holiday-2025-sale/1100-6536986/">Target's Best Exclusive Lego Sets Get Rare Holiday Discounts</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/best-xbox-elite-series-2-wireless-controller-deal-holiday-2025/1100-6535861/">Xbox Elite Series 2 Controllers On Sale For Even Better Prices Than Black Friday Deals</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/final-fantasy-i-vi-collection-anniversary-edition-pixel-remasters-nintendo-switch-playstation-best-amazon-deal/1100-6527670/">Final Fantasy I-VI Pixel Remaster Collection Is Back On Sale For Black Friday Price</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/official-nintendo-switch-2-wheel-set-for-mario-kart-gets-first-discount-at-amazon/1100-6536789/">Nintendo Switch 2 Racing Wheel Set Drops To $20 For A Limited Time</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/asus-rog-xbox-ally-handheld-gaming-pc-holiday-amazon-deal/1100-6536577/">ROG Xbox Ally Gaming Handheld Is On Sale For Only $489 For A Limited Time</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/super-mario-galaxy-rosalina-storybook-nintendo-switch-book-deal/1100-6534724/">Super Mario Galaxy: Rosalina's Storybook Gets 30% Price Cut At Amazon</a></li>   </ul> </div>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
